==Finnish==

===Denominal suffix===
'''-lainen''' (''in words with back vowel harmony'')

'''-läinen''' (''in words with front vowel harmony'')

# Forms the [[inhabitant]] of a place
#: ''[[Viro]]'' "Estonia" -&gt; ''[[virolainen]]'' "Estonian" (''person and adjective'')
# Forms the adjective for a follower of philosophy etc. based on a personal or place name.
#: ''Hegel'' -&gt; ''hegeliläinen''

====Declension====

<table cellpadding="4">
<tr><td>{{Fi38a|-lai}}</td><td> {{Fi38b|-läi}}</td></tr>
</table>

====Usage====
Usually appended to the genitive singular stem, and forms adjectives that can be used as nouns.

